      "text": "func chomp(s string) string {\n\tfor len(s) \u003e 0 \u0026\u0026 (s[len(s)-1] == '\\n' || s[len(s)-1] == '\\r') {\n\t\ts = s[:len(s)-1]\n\t}\n\treturn s\n}",
      "contextualizedText": "// internal/index/manager_test.go \u003e function chomp\n\nfunc chomp(s string) string {\n\tfor len(s) \u003e 0 \u0026\u0026 (s[len(s)-1] == '\\n' || s[len(s)-1] == '\\r') {\n\t\ts = s[:len(s)-1]\n\t}\n\treturn s\n}",
