      "text": "// recordingContextModel wraps a mock model and records the documents passed to\n// EmbedDocument so tests can assert windowing and that the whole-document path\n// was taken.\ntype recordingContextModel struct {\n\t*embed.MockModel\n\tmu   sync.Mutex\n\tdocs []string\n}",
      "contextualizedText": "// internal/index/manager_test.go \u003e type recordingContextModel\n\n// recordingContextModel wraps a mock model and records the documents passed to\n// EmbedDocument so tests can assert windowing and that the whole-document path\n// was taken.\ntype recordingContextModel struct {\n\t*embed.MockModel\n\tmu   sync.Mutex\n\tdocs []string\n}",
